              "text": "**Planning updates for index and sitemap**\n\nI think I need to patch the index and sitemap, possibly using Python for raw processing. It seems I'll have to utilize the terminal for calculations, especially for word count afterwards. I might want to execute code to update both the index and sitemap, but direct writing could also work. I should ensure the Palworld requirements I reference are accurate for 2026, but I’m not entirely clear if my general knowledge is enough. A web search could help, but my tools don’t seem to have the capability for that."
