              "text": "**Exploring document fetching methods**\n\nI’m considering using a terminal with Python requests to fetch official documents, maybe from the Steam page. Then again, I might not need to do that if I can use something like `curl`. I’m thinking we could also use the `mcp_windows` scrape if needed, but I'm leaning toward checking the official page first. Let’s see how this goes!"
