      "reasoning": "**Exploring content options**\n\nI think I need to load a pure HTML affiliate content factory, especially since I’m focusing on relevant content for multiple articles. The user mentioned an image, but maybe I could use existing ones or keep it simple without images? I should check if the template includes emoji icons but not images. It might be worth inspecting options for loading pure HTML and looking into website-building and SEO considerations as well.",
